                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18320405-276-off1615 t18320405-276-cd1616"></join>, 1 table-spoon, value 8s., and 1 handkerchief, value 3s., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18320405-276-victim2323" type="victimName">
